# Codex / OpenAI codex-rs vendored components

This directory contains Apache-2.0 licensed sandbox components vendored from
the OpenAI Codex project (codex-rs), adapted for Codeteam as `codeteam-*` crates.

See LICENSE in this directory for the full Apache License 2.0 text.

Modifications include:
- Crate renaming (`codex-*` → `codeteam-*`)
- Integration with Codeteam `SandboxPolicy` / NAPI launcher
- Slimmed `codeteam-sandbox-policy` for task-level policy compilation

Original source reference:
`https://github.com/openai/codex`
